Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, Omashola on Thursday revealed why fellow housemate Mercy would have poisoned him in the reality show. Omashola speaking to Seyi after Thursday task which had his team lose, told him that Mercy is a cunning woman. According to him, “Mercy would not do anything to make others and another team win. “She would have poisoned me in this house if I put her up for eviction with my Veto power. I know that girl.” Meanwhile, Team legend on Thursday night emerged winners of wager task after both teams put up drama performances showing four elements of drama as instructed by Biggie. VIDEO:   A post shared by gists box (@bbnaija2019gists) on Sep 12, 2019 at 4:06pm PDT  Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.